<p><b>Persecution of Jews</b> has occurred on numerous occasions and at widely different geographical locations. As well as being a major component in <a href="/wiki/Jewish_history" title="Jewish history">Jewish history</a>, it has significantly affected the general history and social development of the countries and societies in which the persecuted Jews lived.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
<td>
<div id="toctitle">
